high-tech houses, but problems have surfaced elsewhere. (Crabb,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   AIRFORCEONE01 _ DAYTON, Ohio _ In the movie Air Force One ,
Russian terrorists run amok on the president's Boeing 747 and take
the chief executive and his family hostage. So much for Hollywood
soundstages. Anyone who attempts to run amok on the Air Force One
now displayed at the U.S. Air Force Museum may run headlong into a
plexiglass wall. (Hopkins, Dayton Daily News) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   KITCHEN-HAIR _ 10 kitchen-related beauty tips, i.e. using coffee
to darken hair, lemon juice to lighten it, etc. (Edwards, Palm
Beach Post). MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   MANGOS-IDEAS _ 40 ways to use your mangoes. (Norris, Palm Beach
Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   WITH
</P>
<P>
   MANGOS-RECIPES.
</P>
<P>
   FIREWORKS01 _ Oooooo! Aaahhhh! If that's the extent of your
fireworks commentary, help has arrived. Pay attention as Professor
Pyro teaches us Fireworks Appreciation. Then use your newfound
knowledge to wow your wife, show off for your kids, impress your
friends. They'll ooooo and aaahhhh at your brilliant bursts of
intellect. Here's a closer look at a few of the bursts you're
likely to see. (Franquet, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
