   What you thought you heard: ``Big boys, stay quiet.''
</P>
<P>
   The actual lyric: ``Big boys don't cry.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Spirit In The Sky,'' Norman Greenbaum
</P>
<P>
   What you thought you heard: ``I got a friend in cheeses.''
</P>
<P>
   The actual lyric: ``I got a friend in Jesus.''
</P>
<P>
   ``Radar Love,'' Golden EarringWhat you thought you heard: ``Been
driving all night/My aunt's sweat on the wheel.''
</P>
<P>
   The actual lyric: ``Been driving all night/My hand's wet on the
wheel.''
</P>
<P>
   NAME THAT '70s TUNE
</P>
