professor Ray Berta, a Roman Catholic brother, might be the
Unabomber. Brother Ray is OK now, but for a while there, the man of
God's mild clerical demeanor went on sabbatical and he stormed
about the college's campus breathing fire and brimstone. By SCOTT
WINOKUR.
</P>
