   &UR; CLINTON IN CHINA &LR;  (``i'' category code)
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-CLINTON (Shanghai) _ The president's day: Talk radio with
Chinese characteristics, other doings. By Seth Faison.
</P>
<P>
