By John M. Broder.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-TAIWAN (Shanghai) _ President Clinton, in a concession to
Beijing, re-states America's opposition to independence for Taiwan.
By John M. Broder.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-PEONY (Shanghai) _ Developments in the tour controversy:
It doesn't look good for ``Peony Pavilion.'' By Seth Faison.
</P>
<P>
   HONGKONG-ANNIVERSARY (Hong Kong) _ Amid economic uncertainty,
Hong Kong prepares to mark a year of Chinese rule. By Mark Landler.
</P>
