<HEADLINE>
DRUG-RESISTANT AIDS VIRUS SEEN AS TRANSMITTABLE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (a and i coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By RICHARD A. KNOX  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
<P>
   GENEVA _ AIDS specialists had hoped it wouldn't happen, but now,
