<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-30 21:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4704 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ELIMINATE-CHINA-EXILE     06-30 0031
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-ELIMINATE-CHINA-EXILES-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
ATTN EDITORS:  

</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
