   EATERY-PLACARDS (Los Angeles) _ The city's new grading system
for restaurant hygiene is having a big impact: The grade cards are
being stolen right out of restaurant windows. Officials say other
restaurants with lower letter grades
</P>
<P>
   and souvenir hunters are likely culprits. By Lee Condon. (Will
move in the ``n'' California news file.)
</P>
