<HEADLINE>
MCVEIGH LETTERS TO FAMILY ARE PORTRAIT OF ANGER AND ALIENATION 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Subs to clarify language in 10th graf)  (With MCVEIGH-TEXT) 
<TEXT>
<P>
