<HEADLINE>
MENTAL ABUSE CAN LEAVE DEEPER SCARS THAN PHYSICAL MISTREATMENT 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By GINGER SCOTT  
 c.1998 The Arizona Republic  
