</P>
<P>
   (NYT1) NEW YORK -- June 30, 1998 -- FANCY-FOOD-SHOW, 6-30 --
Chef Alain Rondelli and Brook Carey presenting his cooking sauces
at the Fancy Food Show. Chefs may want to get you into their
restaurants, but now more than ever, they have their eye on your
pantry shelf as well. The chefs, and their product lines, are out
in force at this year's annual trade show at the Jacob K. Javits
Convention Center, ending Sunday afternoon. (Dith Pran/New York
Times Photo)
</P>
<P>
   The New York Times News Service
