   Vietnam's Hotel Sofitel Metropole Hanoi has a special business
traveler's package that includes a buffet breakfast, a fruit
basket, late check-out, free laundry and pressing, discounted dry
cleaning and free local phone calls. Rates, good through Dec. 31,
are $229 a night single occupancy and $259 double occupancy, not
including service or tax. &QL;
</P>
<P>
   --- &QL;
</P>
<P>
   As of next Tuesday, U S Airways will no longer issue advance
boarding passes to its passengers.
</P>
<P>
   &QL;
</P>
</TEXT>
